!**/packages/*/build/
!**/packages/*/buildMultiTargeting/
!**/packages/*/buildTransitive/

# --- .NET User Secrets ---
secrets.json
**/secrets.json

# --- Global .NET CLI artifacts ---
.project
global.json.user
.dotnet/

